<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，德克摇响了铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“仆人和骑士到宴会厅去！”他大声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出事了。”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跟着大家去了宴会厅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有条龙正在逼近皇宫。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它会喷火！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都吓了一跳。“火？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“骑士们，爬上最高的塔楼。”国王命令道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好你们的剑，扔向那条龙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，陛下！”骑士们迅速离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“仆人们，找些大石头来。”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用石头扔向那条龙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，陛下！”仆人们迅速离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，国王也大步走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆看着德克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“需要我用魔法吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用！”德克皱着眉头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是个大问题，魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你就待在这里！别添麻烦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克也离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆生气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用力踢了墙一脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢！我的脚！”汤姆大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>挂毯从墙上掉下来，掉在汤姆身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪从他的口袋里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还好吗？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还好。”汤姆点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是皇家魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想帮忙赶走那条龙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就去帮忙啊。”猫咪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“德克让我留在......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173529</EndMilliseconds>
